rwise suspiciously\ncircular orbit. This reinforces the point that the full complement of planets\nin a system is needed to assess its dynamical state.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Dec 2015 18:31:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-27"}
