ation of boundary-operator and short-distance expansions, proper\nextensions of inverse scattering theory, new trace formulae, and semiclassical\nexpansions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Dec 2015 10:39:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Feb 2017 13:23:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-17"}
