. A. Lopez-Marcos, and J. M. Sanz-Serna. Results of\nsimulations are compared with that of evolution of corresponding impulse in the\ngranular pre-stressed chain.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Dec 2015 15:44:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-22"}
